The paper focuses on developing an Arabic Questions Answering System based on entailment metrics, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. The system also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the system is designed for Arabic language, which could also fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
